  <name>Darhon Finance</name>
  <summary>Manage your personal accounts</summary>

  <description>
    <p>A robust user-friendly personal finance program to track your credit cards, bank accounts and investments.</p>
    <p>It is packed with multiple currency capability, bank reconciliation, split transactions, reports and graphs.</p>
    <p>Simplify your search by filtering transactions or search them with a powerful in-built tool.</p>
    <p>Export transactions to TXT or print them to PDF file.</p>
    <p>Set up your budget and plan for your expenses.</p>
    <p>Register scheduled transactions for recurrent operations.</p>
    <p>Safebox module is included to keep your private data stored in only one place.</p>
    <p>Optimized for desktop computers.</p>
  </description>

